description.narrative: Regional Representation, Advocacy and Partnership Promotion, Programme Guidance, Quality Assurance and Oversight provided for effective equity-focused YCSD response to development and humanitarian challenges in line with corporate strategy and guidelines., which contributes to Child Health, Operations Support To Programme Delivery, Technical Excellence In Policy And Programmes. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Developing And Leveraging Resources And Partnerships, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: ESA country offices and development partners support the development and implementation of equity-based and child rights sensitive national policies, development plans and strategies, UN joint frameworks, UNICEF country programmes and Inter-Agency humanitarian action plans towards improved results for children.
